21:43.369 --> 21:46.138 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
on.

21:46.172 --> 21:48.274 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It's interesting material.

21:48.307 --> 21:56.081 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have done enough work now
