with the material's
authenticity.

21:56.115 --> 22:03.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so now it's a matter of
completing the
format, layout to make it easy
and accessible

22:03.422 --> 22:10.729 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
