Committee have resigned.

22:21.440 --> 22:27.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What would you consider the
successful outcome,
the most damage that could be
done from this?

22:27.780 --> 22:31.083 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JULIAN ASSANGE: Well, WikiLeaks
began 10 years.

22:31.116 --> 22:37.556 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We take leaks, principally from
whistle-blowers,
of material that is of
diplomatic, political,

22:37.590 --> 22:41.827 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
