22:43.062 --> 22:45.965 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we publish it and we write
analysis about
it.

22:45.998 --> 22:53.639 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And we also engineer
globe-spanning media
collaborations in order to get
the best understanding

22:53.672 --> 22:55.641 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of that material.

22:55.674 --> 23:01.513 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we place it in our library,
which is available
to everyone, has more than 10
million documents

23:01.547 --> 23:06.218 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in it now which we feel that
otherwise would
not have come before the public,
and that

23:06.252 --> 23:11.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
performs an ongoing role leading
to great
works in investigative
journalism, successful

23:11.857 --> 23:20.165 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
