of political
competition.

23:24.136 --> 23:29.441 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, let me ask
you about
that, about the -- what you
consider a successful

23:29.475 --> 23:35.314 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
