24:24.830 --> 24:26.832 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I think that's a very
interesting question.

24:26.865 --> 24:34.473 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, my position, as an analyst
is that, yes,
that Hillary Clinton is a war
hawk.

24:34.506 --> 24:41.280 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the statement was made
within the context
of the early phases of the
Democratic primaries.

24:41.313 --> 24:44.083 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It is by no means an endorsement
of Donald
Trump.

24:44.116 --> 24:47.886 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But you still
