36:57.282 --> 36:58.416 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
There is a list.

36:58.450 --> 37:00.785 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Every state identifies you
somehow.

37:00.819 --> 37:02.720 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It might be that you give your
signature.

37:02.754 --> 37:05.190 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And if it's that, then your
signature is on
the line.

37:05.223 --> 37:06.324 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
You're already voted.

37:06.357 --> 37:08.059 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
You can't vote 10 times.

37:08.093 --> 37:11.629 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I would say it was a silly thing
to say, except
I think it's really dangerous to
call the

37:11.663 --> 37:16.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
